    {
      "id": "68c36b07-a518-479b-b23c-f702c662276b",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$A = \\begin{pmatrix}1 &       &(2)\\cr\n                     &\\ddots     \\cr\n                  (2)&       &1  \\cr\\end{pmatrix}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(A = \\begin{pmatrix}1\n&amp;       &amp;(2)\\cr\n                     &amp;\\ddots     \\cr\n                  (2)&amp;       &amp;1  \\cr\\end{pmatrix}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "a33e5654-3edb-44d1-9b27-c6b0f3cbe5b7",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\begin{pmatrix} a & &b    \\cr\n                          &\\ddots \\cr\n                        b & &a    \\cr\\end{pmatrix}$ avec\n            $\\begin{cases} a = \\frac1n\\bigl( (2n-1)^k + (n-1)(-1)^k \\bigr) \\cr\n                     b = \\frac1n\\bigl( (2n-1)^k -      (-1)^k \\bigr).\\cr \\end{cases}$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\begin{pmatrix} a &amp; &amp;b    \\cr\n                          &amp;\\ddots \\cr\n                        b &amp; &amp;a    \\cr\\end{pmatrix}\\)</span> avec\n<span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\begin{cases} a = \\frac1n\\bigl( (2n-1)^k +\n(n-1)(-1)^k \\bigr) \\cr\n                     b = \\frac1n\\bigl( (2n-1)^k -      (-1)^k \\bigr).\\cr\n\\end{cases}\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2a073021-8d3e-497c-9e7e-2a5cd3ccedf4",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$A = \\begin{pmatrix} 1 &2 &3 &4 \\cr\n                    0 &1 &2 &3 \\cr\n                    0 &0 &1 &2 \\cr\n                    0 &0 &0 &1 \\cr \\end{pmatrix}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(A = \\begin{pmatrix} 1 &amp;2 &amp;3\n&amp;4 \\cr\n                    0 &amp;1 &amp;2 &amp;3 \\cr\n                    0 &amp;0 &amp;1 &amp;2 \\cr\n                    0 &amp;0 &amp;0 &amp;1 \\cr\n\\end{pmatrix}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
