        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\begin{pmatrix} 1 &amp;2k &amp;2k^2+k\n&amp;\\frac 13(4k^3 + 6k^2 + 2k) \\cr\n                       0\n&amp;1  &amp;2k     &amp;2k^2+k                     \\cr\n                       0\n&amp;0  &amp;1      &amp;2k                         \\cr\n                       0\n&amp;0  &amp;0      &amp;1                          \\cr\n\\end{pmatrix}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
